{"tid":2430430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英台民間聲援：千祈唔好慣  許智峯倫敦為戰友集氣","createTime":"2021-03-03T02:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T02:38:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"24af8108f181d459a84427684e223373d95b9cd2","tid":2430430,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:30:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/5UECF4WKNNCMHJWRQVBXA26O6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2F5UECF4WKNNCMHJWRQVBXA26O6U%2F&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiunXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=3710095d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2F5UECF4WKNNCMHJWRQVBXA26O6U%2F&h=62e2fe33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/5UECF4WKNNCMHJWRQVBXA26O6U/</a><br />\n<br />\n英台民間聲援：千祈唔好慣 <br />\n許智峯倫敦為戰友集氣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yQtR8Lt2IyNsF-dMrZK5IGq86iA=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QOZEP6X43VFRTGBG5XMJQVVP3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyQtR8Lt2IyNsF-dMrZK5IGq86iA%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQOZEP6X43VFRTGBG5XMJQVVP3A.jpg&h=59a467cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【曼徹斯特】■近百人在嚴格封鎖措施下出席集會撐港，有參加者高舉「五一」手勢。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府以港版國安法檢控47名去年參與立法會民主派初選的人士串謀顛覆國家政權罪，觸發港人及國際社會反彈，英國和台灣均有集會聲援被捕人士。流亡海外的立法會前議員許智峯亦有現身倫敦集會，表明海外港人不會放棄，「我哋會撐到最後」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：不人道聆訊 47子受折磨24小時<br />\n<br />\n居英港人Oreo和Coco前日出席曼徹斯特的集會，其間與會人士高叫口號、高舉「五一」手勢，並合唱《願榮光歸香港》。由於疫情關係，當地實施嚴格的封鎖措施，因此集會不足一小時便要完結；即使如此，仍有約100人堅持出席，令Oreo和 Coco覺得「好感動」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Er2YCfUHVp8enk2lbZt_gPaDhBE=/1181x977/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/34ZAXNRLYNEVXM2J5M7MKQJNUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEr2YCfUHVp8enk2lbZt_gPaDhBE%3D%2F1181x977%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F34ZAXNRLYNEVXM2J5M7MKQJNUE.jpg&h=5eaf9f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【倫敦】■流亡英國的立法會前議員許智峯（右）現身集會，強調會繼續對外為港人發聲。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記掛同路人無法入眠<br />\n<br />\n二人已移居曼徹斯特一年多，2019年反送中運動令她們無悔來英，坦言近日看到《蘋果》新聞「好火滾同時亦好難過」，但自覺「千祈唔好慣」，又表示即使身在英國，港人仍然關心香港，「想同47位（被告）講，遠在英國都有好多同路人撐你哋，願你哋平安回家」。<br />\n<br />\n倫敦市中心亦有數十人集會，。。。。。。。。。。其間眾人又高呼「光復香港，時代革命」、「五大訴求，缺一不可」等口號，約半小時後散去。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯亦有出席倫敦的集會，。。。。。。。。。。「撐咗幾十年嘅老朋友」，「我想佢哋知道，無論如何我哋都會撐到最後，我哋唔會放棄」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/E58l6uBgIOS50kogg0XEvkGjo0E=/1181x812/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SDPYYUCNIJBOZITAFRNN7JMSKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FE58l6uBgIOS50kogg0XEvkGjo0E%3D%2F1181x812%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSDPYYUCNIJBOZITAFRNN7JMSKE.jpg&h=75dcc5d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【倫敦】■市中心集會上有多人舉起「光時」旗幟，並高唱《願榮光歸香港》。<br />\n<br />\n另外，台灣學聯、經濟民主連合等近20個民間團體昨在台北立法院群賢樓前召開記者會，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n曾在中大就讀的陳薇安現為台大香港研究社社長，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n由於47名香港民主派人士被落案起訴串謀顛覆國家政權罪當日，正值是台灣二二八事件74周年，台灣人特別感慨良多。1947年2月28日，不滿緝私人員暴力執法的台灣民眾上街示威，卻遭到國民黨政府開槍射殺，持續幾個月的鎮壓有多達2.8萬台灣本土精英遭屠殺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Az5WHvIulwJfl-uEM8d9I-9MCCI=/1482x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KVYACM2TXFEELDU7OND7VCEK7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAz5WHvIulwJfl-uEM8d9I-9MCCI%3D%2F1482x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKVYACM2TXFEELDU7OND7VCEK7Y.jpg&h=8953fc54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【台北】■多個團體在立法院前開記者會，呼籲修例庇護流亡港人。台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"8981b8ad3e7698ace749f13390c5c03155eb6bd2","tid":2430430,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:35:24.000Z","msg":"許勇峯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccc2cb8c748d582d49f7425de1d3211af7d6a5b","tid":2430430,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e85bd48060bddc76e0f19afe7b0f7ff0f39c88","tid":2430430,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:38:37.000Z","msg":"好波"}]}